  "prompt": "What resorts in Renuka Lake Tourist-spots would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "Renuka Lake, located in Himachal Pradesh, India, is a scenic destination that appeals to many tourists for its natural beauty. When it comes to finding accommodations that are friendly and safe for unmarried couples, consider the following options:\n\n1. **Private Resorts**: Look for private resorts or guesthouses that advertise themselves as couple-friendly. Some resorts are known for their privacy and a more relaxed atmosphere.\n\n2. **Homestays**: Opting for homestays can provide a more personal experience, and many hosts are accommodating towards unmarried couples. Ensure you check reviews beforehand to find places with a good reputation for privacy and support for all guests.\n\n3. **Online Platforms**: Websites like OYO Rooms, Airbnb, and MakeMyTrip allow you to filter for couple-friendly accommodations. Always read recent reviews and make sure the place explicitly states it is welcoming to unmarried couples.\n\n4. **Reputed Hotels**: Some chain hotels may also be a safer bet, as they tend to have standardized policies around guest accommodation that might provide added comfort.\n\nBefore booking, consider contacting the property directly to inquire about their policies regarding unmarried couples. This can give you peace of mind and help ensure a hassle-free stay. Lastly, being respectful of local customs and norms can go a long way in ensuring a positive experience during your trip.",
